title: West Sussex mother left with ROTTING breasts avoids death | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Mother-of-two is left with ROTTING breasts after silicone implants leaked into her blood stream - as cosmetic procedures fall to a ten-year low in the UK WARNING GRAPHIC CONTENT: Annette Stevens, 48, from West Sussex, had implants more than 13 years ago after breastfeeding left her with 'saggy' breasts But silicone leaked into her blood stream causing a range of health problems In 2016, a surgeon confirmed Annette had suffered a 'severe gel bleed' Published: 09:33 GMT, 14 February 2017 | Updated: 12:12 GMT, 14 February 2017 268 shares
